com.konakartadmin.app
Class AdminAddressSearchResult

java.lang.Object
  com.konakartadmin.app.AdminAddressSearchResult

public class AdminAddressSearchResult
extends java.lang.Object

This is the object returned for API calls returning an array of AdminAddresses. It contains an array of AdminAddress objects and the total number of AdminAdresses matching the request, so that they can be paged.
